name: The Birth of Earthly Delight #1
description:
Nika Volchek
2021

"The Birth of Earthly Delight" series made in mixed media format. It's a mix of photography, painting and digital.
The image that runs through all the works is the apotheosis of the unconsious mind. It symbolizes the unknown forms within us. The artist shows a picture of what is happening under this state.

6531 x 9797px.
